description: Calling all first time home buyers and investors! This beautiful 1 bed 1 bath is in an A+ Southie location walkable to all the shops and restaurants that line Broadway as well as multiple MBTA bus lines, Castle Island, the beach and more! This unit offers hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, granite counters and a convenient pantry. The bedroom is king sized and has a built out closet. Private laundry can be found in the basement along with additional storage space. Central air and low condo fees make this a great opportunity. Don't miss out!
